OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FTwo men who kidnapped and violently
OL,7,Fattacked an elderly imam before trying
OL,8,Fto cover it up by setting fire to the
OL,9,Fcar they used have been jailed.
OL,11,FThe 87-year-old was taken from the
OL,12,Fstreets in Oldham, bundled into the
OL,13,Fback of an Audi, blindfolded and
OL,14,Frepeatedly punched, strangled and hit
OL,15,Fwith a stick.
