OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FAfter a "sustained and violent
OL,7,Fbeating", he was then stripped to just
OL,8,Fhis underpants and a 'torn and blood-
OL,9,Fstained' tee shirt and dumped on a
OL,10,Fcold and remote country road in the
OL,11,FRishworth area of West Yorkshire.
OL,13,FManchester Crown Court heard how
OL,14,FAzizur Rahman and his friend Shohad
OL,15,FMiah carried out the kidnap in
OL,16,FSeptember 2024 after they learned the
OL,17,Felderly man had performed a 'ritual
OL,18,Fexorcism' on Rahman's stepson because
OL,19,Fhe was "believed to be possessed by
OL,20,Fevil spirits".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
