OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FThe imam had been asked by Rahman's
OL,7,Festranged wife to visit their home
OL,8,Fwhere he said prayers and provided
OL,9,Famulets.
OL,11,FAfter being dumped in the street the
OL,12,Felderly victim was forced to walk for
OL,13,Faround half an hour wearing only one
OL,14,Fshoe before he knocked on at a house
OL,15,Ffor help, and the emergency services
OL,16,Fwere called.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
