OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FHe was left with a number of injuries
OL,7,Fincluding a bleed on the brain, a
OL,8,Fbloody wound to his ear, a swelling to
OL,9,Fhis cheekbone, a large bruise to his
OL,10,Fneck and a missing tooth.
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement read out
OL,13,Fin court, he said the incident had
OL,14,Fleft him feeling "shameful in my own
OL,15,Fcommunity".
OL,17,FHe said: "Before the incident, I used
OL,18,Fto go out of the house regularly and
OL,19,Fspeak with members of the community. I
OL,20,Fdon't go out as often anymore.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
