OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,F"When I do, I feel a great sense of
OL,7,Fshame over what happened to me. I am
OL,8,Fwell known in the community and lots
OL,9,Fof people ask me what happened.
OL,11,F"I get a sense from speaking to people
OL,12,Fthat they assume I must have done
OL,13,Fsomething wrong to be treated in such
OL,14,Fa way. This makes me feel shameful in
OL,15,Fmy own community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
