OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,F"Before this happened, I used to walk
OL,7,Fto mosque every day by myself with
OL,8,Ffreedom and I would look forward to
OL,9,Fgoing. Now, even though I still walk
OL,10,Fto mosque by myself, I feel scared in
OL,11,Fcase something like this happens again.
OL,13,F"I have been scared ever since this
OL,14,Fhappened and am still not sleeping
OL,15,Fwell. At night, I keep thinking about
OL,16,Fwhat happened to me and it keeps me
OL,17,Fawake as I run it through in my mind."
OL,19,FOn Tuesday 15 July, the cocaine-
OL,20,Ffuelled kidnappers were jailed
OL,21,Ffollowing the terrifying attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
