OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FRahman, 39, of Bluebell Walk, St
OL,7,FMary's Way, Oldham, who the court
OL,8,Fheard had 20 previous convictions for
OL,9,F30 offences and was at the time
OL,10,Fserving a suspended prison sentence
OL,11,Ffor drink driving, was sentenced to 11
OL,12,Fyears and 16 weeks in prison after
OL,13,Fbeing found guilty of kidnap, robbery,
OL,14,Fsection 18 assault, intentional
OL,15,Fstrangulation and perverting the
OL,16,Fcourse of justice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
