OL,6,FMiah, 25, of Firbank Road, Royton, was
OL,7,Fjailed for nine years after being
OL,8,Ffound guilty of kidnap, section 20
OL,9,Fassault, intentional strangulation and
OL,10,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,12,FSpeaking after the case Det Sgt Rick
OL,13,FBolt, of GMP's Major Incident Team,
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was a particularly
OL,15,Fshocking crime that targeted a
OL,16,Fvulnerable elderly man, causing him
OL,17,Fsevere physical and emotional trauma.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
