OL,3,CElderly imam 'begged and pleaded for
OL,4,Cmercy' during attack
OL,6,FThis was not a random attack; the
OL,7,Fvictim was specifically targeted due
OL,8,Fto a prior visit to Rahman's home,
OL,9,Fwhere he had performed prayers:
OL,11,F"The swift and thorough investigation
OL,12,Fby our team, utilising forensic
OL,13,Fevidence, ensured that these dangerous
OL,14,Findividuals were brought to justice.
OL,16,F"We hope this sentence provides some
OL,17,Fmeasure of comfort to the victim and
OL,18,Fhis family and serves as a stark
OL,19,Fwarning to those who think they can
OL,20,Fcommit such brutal acts without
OL,21,Fconsequence."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
